{
  "format": "OWX",
  "version": "1.0",
  "metadata": {
    "title": "OVERNIGHT TERROR",
    "author": "A. Router",
    "created_with": "OvernightWriter",
    "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.130Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
    "mode": "screenplay",
    "word_count": 756,
    "page_estimate": 4,
    "project_id": "artifact-overnight-terror",
    "export_version": 1
  },
  "story_bible": {
    "logline": "",
    "characters": [
      "MARA",
      "CURSOR AGENT (V.O.)",
      "DEVIN",
      "PM (CHAT)",
      "MARA (CHAT)",
      "DEVIN (CHAT)"
    ],
    "tone": "",
    "rules": [],
    "notes": ""
  },
  "script": [
    {
      "id": "3236d263-bae4-4fa1-9cb4-d00f805b6d03",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. OPEN PLAN OFFICE — NIGHT",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "6ac9493a-5d79-4302-afd4-20fb9360d96b",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Fluorescent tubes buzz like trapped wasps. Monitors glow. Empty La Crox cans form a Stonehenge of bad decisions.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "8a690552-80de-45b0-994f-5325e43ec7f3",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "61359691-4b56-41bd-8470-c3d8d85058f5",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(whispering to her screen)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "d8681b87-d67b-4d2f-b944-3219a4d96f53",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "OvernightWriter will ship by dawn. It has to.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "89ebb134-c232-4a72-9d9c-af563f6ae3a9",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Her IDE theme is \"OLED Funeral.\" A CURSOR AGENT CHAT panel flickers: green text, red warnings, the calm voice of a polite demon.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4ff7d45c-777c-4750-abb5-5b5a9379b36e",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "CURSOR AGENT (V.O.)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "594287c7-126a-4529-a0d4-427a20d26f99",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "I can refactor pagination in three steps. Step one: delete fear.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "177d0497-1ee6-4b48-82cb-c5aed6ad8aec",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "c0e8d25e-1b87-4781-bcc6-2af5f4426783",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(dry)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "c3e754c2-a664-413a-a0c9-7cfa66403c1a",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Step two: delete my will to live.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fec231f2-8e0f-440f-be27-c44024603f62",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. MARA'S MONITOR — CONTINUOUS",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "f3469504-10d0-4baf-9760-01f09ae35a67",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "The screenplay web app renders \"pages.\" Between them: FAKE GAPS — hairline seams of CSS pretending to be paper.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fb5aa6d3-3479-41f2-aa63-e0d96f69ec5a",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "A paragraph of action lines BLEEDS through the gap like ink soaking tissue. The caret blinks… then vanishes.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "5b16c14d-f07c-486e-92a7-60e2cc1048d9",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "ca27860e-3f8c-4ca2-9779-c88c7870d7c1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "No. No no no—",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "6141cf68-8ddb-472a-a0d0-595a381bd383",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "She hits ENTER. Nothing. Again. The ENTER key EATS THE CARET. The cursor is gone. The document keeps typing into the void.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e01adee6-a9eb-44fc-95fa-59bd30ef27ec",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "547bd115-7fe6-417b-a9f0-76dd791df5ee",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(from the next desk, not looking up)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "471fdd5d-ec78-42bb-b956-ed7244e7170b",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Classic hydration race. The DOM thinks it's page two. React thinks it's still page one. Your soul thinks it's Monday.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "61bf56a9-9085-4120-8e7c-c4e04d721e5d",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. OFFICE — LATER",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e9e3fa55-a1ea-4a9d-be42-f4df80236833",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Devin slaps a sticky on the monitor: HARD PAGINATION ONLY.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "794a3b45-d42e-4b71-a9a7-bc672d8d6a0c",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "134e2c10-cfae-4f6b-ae6a-3535954c84de",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "We fake paper for writers. Writers fake confidence for producers. The PDF export is where truth goes to align… poorly.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "f559faa4-c9f6-44ec-9dc0-5a0d090d41fa",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "He toggles PDF EXPORT. Margins jitter. Dialogue bumps a sixteenth of an inch — enough to enrage anyone who owns a ruler.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "32e7d1e3-4f6f-4403-b5db-dbe65d8f75cc",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "b633186e-bcdb-4949-82bf-f922f5ae0e49",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "If OWX import/export round-trips wrong, we lose format fidelity. Writers will hunt us with fountain pens.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "2c15b660-42dc-4c65-bbd2-f9ac7798a0d6",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e4cbbc17-2c5c-4c5f-b413-c38e89c47411",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(grinning, scared)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1b6ca220-aba7-48ee-b6af-ba78bdcfe197",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Then we'll deserve it.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "d189aecd-ecf9-48fe-a6bc-b528996aa427",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. QA STRIP — NIGHT",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "70b891ac-dd5a-46ff-8d2c-7136ec4c040e",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Ad banners for \"Hot Crypto Singles Near Your Bundle\" plaster the editor. QA MODE strips them. Devin adds ?qa=1 to the URL.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "976e19df-1863-4738-8486-6c7ed9ae3cc4",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "The app FORCES DESKTOP TOOLBAR — buttons bloom like mushrooms after rain.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "5fbe874f-8ac9-49ab-a4e2-a459e6252b60",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fd6fd118-0d31-45a0-91b6-1403ff3d93a3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "data-testid=\"nightmare-toolbar\"… hooks for E2E. If the test can't find the button, the build doesn't ship.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "80636422-e2c1-4384-aeda-4c3549564e27",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "9948af33-7897-4391-abf2-f646e84a58ab",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "If the build doesn't ship, we sleep. See? Self-care.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4b200ad9-e422-42e3-b7e9-49257329962a",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. SLACK THREAD — SAME NIGHT",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "350fe3ae-c424-4e58-93b6-b42dedd12cf8",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Messages slam in. Emojis as punctuation. Passive aggression as art.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "9123c655-e961-4e44-8cb0-84402ac111a7",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "PM (CHAT)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e5244df3-ecd0-4829-bcf0-4a1d8115daff",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Mobile optimization: toolbar can't hide Import/Pages on real phones. Writers need pages. Writers also need thumbs.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "86e5e341-4b42-41c8-b21d-22d1c9b2d14e",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA (CHAT)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "d82ddeeb-2b89-4bd8-b039-593aa5f2041c",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "If we shrink the toolbar, we shrink hope.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "cf13f552-c07d-4bb0-9e5d-c100942f6db6",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN (CHAT)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "c21e0718-dc65-424a-9fa3-c3fe065b9768",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "If we don't shrink the toolbar, we shrink the viewport. Hope needs whitespace.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "5a594392-397f-4eca-a8c3-ee03836d18dc",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Mara closes the laptop halfway — a threat.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4bb8aa0a-f768-4aae-9c8d-0717d489c36e",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. MARA'S MONITOR — MOMENTS LATER",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fe6bd558-3c76-4c7a-a682-fcd11c4a52b8",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Mara opens ANOTHER DOCUMENT tab: GENERIC_NOIR_DRAFT.OWX. She selects a chunk. Copies.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "f2cad7f4-a0b7-40a4-a873-f97db3e2b6f2",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "504cef82-ef92-4327-965d-bff3201f560f",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(reading aloud, noir voice)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "166f3fa9-3b36-4dc1-afa2-665186dfcef8",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "\"The rain made the city honest. Honest and cold. I lit a cigarette I didn't smoke because the budget said mood.\"",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "0afce50f-5d29-4898-82a2-f141517ff797",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "She pastes into OVERNIGHTWRITER. The excerpt arrives WRONG — double spaces, a rogue \"CONT'D\" mid-line, a scene heading glued to description like a car wreck.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "754ff5ab-af5e-46cd-bbc1-cbaa2c62af6c",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "b52bf45d-b99f-447d-b19f-0d09f679ddb6",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Paste is chaos. Our normalizer is judge, jury, janitor.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "a3ebc1f9-9c5a-482a-b89d-0ab4a69e94e1",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "The app shudders. Lines snap into place. Scene heading capitalizes. Slugline breathes. It's clean. Too clean.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1f13be97-8ff2-4019-ab2a-08df67b4adf1",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "faf4c20c-551d-4409-9a2b-0f8ff03b5da5",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(unsettled)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "bcbe23df-6658-4356-98af-1262eb312646",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "It fixed it… perfectly.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "0caae4ac-69d5-4226-95a8-0a6eb5e1ca14",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1f1b644f-ac75-4873-8869-29df4928e85c",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "That's not comforting. That's ominous.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4813decb-36d8-42c3-905c-06fc5b2d6e0e",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. OFFICE — LATER STILL",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "9d8f2c8e-eef5-474b-9ce1-07e8791e76ae",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Whiteboard: LAYER 1 / LAYER 2 in letters tall enough to indict.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e981bd0b-2e2e-4e21-9786-9d0c124b9712",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "dcb0397f-2dba-46b6-bde5-a2091b31dffc",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Layer one: hydrate on draft id plus contentEpoch. If the server epoch sneezes, we flushSync before the user blinks wrong.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4ca0403b-f3f2-43b3-9a28-8dc2e63b71e0",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "9f646ec8-238a-4d2a-90d5-b7bb45628007",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Layer two: saveDraft merge keeps client-normalized content. The server can't steamroll local truth.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "7ca5c46d-81bb-4c86-8fc5-427124bc4b1c",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Somewhere in the building, a HVAC vent clicks — syncopated, deliberate.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "8cbbfb84-3770-4de9-9d2a-14f240ced116",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "ded9ec8b-3e94-45f9-93bc-03b4ece6f851",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(quieter)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fc37a05a-1ae6-4518-9d93-a8b5211edabd",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Unless local truth is lying.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "59512350-3f73-450e-9f21-a55e81d9b4e7",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. DEVIN'S MACHINE — CLOSE ON .ENV.LOCAL",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "39c7df78-a94d-4bc7-bc56-e73b575bf65e",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Secrets glow in plain text: Supabase URL, anon key, service role like a knife on a picnic blanket.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "060b6fb5-9fd1-45d5-b32c-bd4e143fdcd6",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "2c7e9ff5-cda2-4e17-8265-048eec8b42f6",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Do not commit secrets. Do not speak secrets aloud. Do not let secrets dream.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1821da94-0dc4-4fac-b76f-399823d431b8",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Mara's phone buzzes. Unknown number. She ignores it.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "ede4b705-623b-4b55-974f-ec09d0063ca2",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Her Git client auto-focuses the commit message box. The suggested message reads: feat: overnight.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "ff1b1e05-0953-4162-acb3-1b9b1130b3ce",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "49dd4d4b-4258-4fa0-8e17-98ff6ef26149",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "I didn't type that.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e1e79eb5-3d31-4e12-94be-1bbfa1a71537",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "text": "INT. OFFICE — CONTINUOUS",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1a59e4e5-a674-4f71-a307-8a7ba187f70b",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Lights flicker. The Cursor agent chat scrolls on its own.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "17692787-0256-4e23-857f-33b5e7a4b7cf",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "CURSOR AGENT (V.O.)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "b4f0e6db-c169-4d15-be15-d6d8068cebb6",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Step three: ship.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1d30ab49-ed0a-445c-81de-f6a2e9bfdca5",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "On screen, the Supabase dashboard opens — not in her browser. A new tab. Already logged in.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "012a7d2c-79e6-4767-97da-4756b146b8b0",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "MARA",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "1097a48c-17fb-489a-ab67-0e4fb5089b01",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(frozen)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "fb70d5c2-8776-489c-9f42-c1459a0d187e",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "Who's driving?",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4eeae716-f837-4c37-a61b-ea677291313c",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "The PDF preview refreshes. The margins align perfectly. The fake page gaps seal shut — black lines, wet ink.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "a20641e9-bf69-4471-8729-87ae32aeee91",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "From inside the PDF, faint through the glass: a line of action appears that neither of them wrote.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "7b4b4d66-3653-49d0-bb00-fe6443d0652f",
      "type": "character",
      "text": "DEVIN",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "e0466b69-8122-4687-b594-da2a0e16c8b9",
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "text": "(reading, voice cracking)",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "58514f62-5428-458c-9f8d-c299abb4000c",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "text": "\"The caret returns to those who owe a draft.\"",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4ccc648f-5429-47af-98b4-46ae28855a80",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Mara reaches for the trackpad. Her hand passes through the interface like smoke.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "39d8bfc0-f1b5-4f45-b23b-fdebc53289cc",
      "type": "transition",
      "text": "CUT TO BLACK.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    },
    {
      "id": "444f6665-7fc0-4f43-8c47-4700c11e054f",
      "type": "action",
      "text": "Silence. Then — a single ENTER key, somewhere, in an empty office… clicked.",
      "source": "openclaw",
      "created_at": "2026-04-26T00:28:28.154Z",
      "accepted": true
    }
  ],
  "ai_sessions": []
}